<text><body>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0924C.0030c" n="0030c"/>
<lb n="0030c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0030c02"/><head type="no">No. 924C</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0030c03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0030031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】大日本續藏經</note>藥師儀軌一具</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0030c04"/>
<lb n="0030c05"/><p>若欲入向道場者。先澡浴清淨。以真言手印。
<lb n="0030c06"/>灑淨所換之衣。次以真言加持其衣而著。真
<lb n="0030c07"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c08"/><p type="dharani">唵微&CB00757;羅莎縛賀</p>
<lb n="0030c09"/><p>次即衣著。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c10"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;哩&CB00085;羅多&CB00085;曰里尼吽</p>
<lb n="0030c11"/><p>次飲水灑淨。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c12"/><p type="dharani">唵摩訶入&CB00085;羅吽</p>
<lb n="0030c13"/><p>次入向道場時。不起貪欲瞋恚等。專念本尊
<lb n="0030c14"/>而住<note place="inline">住自他本清淨。步步想踐連華&CB01191;</note>次至道場門外灑淨<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0030c15"/><p>次香水灑身。以後稱吽字三聲。然後道場并
<lb n="0030c16"/>觀想聖眾。遍滿道場。如影重之。不相妨礙。次
<lb n="0030c17"/>入道場已。面向於本尊。合掌作禮。禮三部尊。
<lb n="0030c18"/>及本尊已。舉頭諦觀佛菩薩金剛像也。向佛
<lb n="0030c19"/>陳說三世宿愆惡障。重懺本尊所。亦如是懺
<lb n="0030c20"/>禮。偈曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c21"/><lg><l>我從過去世</l><l>流轉於生死</l>
<lb n="0030c22"/><l>今對大聖尊</l><l>盡心而懺悔</l>
<lb n="0030c23"/><l>如先佛所懺</l><l>我今亦如是</l>
<lb n="0030c24"/><l>願承加持力</l><l>眾生悉清淨</l>
<lb n="0030c25"/><l>以此大願故</l><l>自他獲無垢</l></lg>
<lb n="0030c26"/><p>次香水淨三業。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c27"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;輸馱薩&CB00085;達麼薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;</p>
<lb n="0030c28"/><p>輸度啥次定心已。作三部三昧耶。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c29"/><p type="dharani">唵怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00617;&CB00418;納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>縛<note place="inline">引</note>也娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">佛</note></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0924C.0031a" n="0031a"/>
<lb n="0031a01"/><p type="dharani">唵跛娜謨<note place="inline">二合</note>納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>縛<note place="inline">引</note>也娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">蓮</note></p>
<lb n="0031a02"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;曰盧<note place="inline">二合</note>納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>縛也婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0031a03"/><p rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">已上三部三昧耶</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031a04"/><p>次遣除身中毘那夜迦。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a05"/><p type="dharani">唵闍波沒&CB00069;帝賀囊迦囊吽泮吒</p>
<lb n="0031a06"/><p>次辟除諸障。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a07"/><p type="dharani">曩謨&CB00085;曰羅也吽賀囊&CB00757;他尾特夢婆輸&CB03586;羅
<lb n="0031a08"/>也泮吒<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031a09"/><p>次辟除諸物所有諸難<note place="inline">在多意云云</note>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a10"/><p type="dharani">唵枳哩枳哩羅&CB00085;嗟捺羅&CB00292;泮吒<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031a11"/><p>次去垢真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a12"/><p type="dharani">唵枳哩枳哩&CB00085;曰羅&CB00292;泮吒<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031a13"/><p>次清淨。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a14"/><p type="dharani">唵爾囊爾迦</p>
<lb n="0031a15"/><p>次光澤。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a16"/><p type="dharani">唵帝誓帝惹徒尾寧徒提沙馱吽泮吒<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031a17"/><p>次神分。次唱禮。一切恭敬。次供文。次四方四
<lb n="0031a18"/>佛四菩薩。次本尊稱名三遍。次三部界會一
<lb n="0031a19"/>切佛菩薩等。次驚覺。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a20"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;曰魯<note place="inline">二合用</note>底瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0031a21"/><p><note place="inline">印者。二手各金剛拳。舒頭指。各頭側相柱二小指相交。每誦一遍。作印拳動</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031a22"/><p>次九方便　至心歸命。</p>
<lb n="0031a23"/><lg><l>歸命十方正等覺</l><l>三世一切具三身</l>
<lb n="0031a24"/><l>歸命一切大乘法</l><l>歸命不退菩提眾</l>
<lb n="0031a25"/><l>歸命諸明真實言</l><l>歸命一切諸密印</l>
<lb n="0031a26"/><l>以身口意清淨業</l><l>慇懃無量恭敬禮</l></lg>
<lb n="0031a27"/><p>歸命頂禮藥師&CB00222;璃光佛。</p>
<lb n="0031a28"/><p>次禮方便。真言曰<note place="inline">印者。以金剛部印。當額誦&CB00057;禮拜</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031a29"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>曩莫薩縛怛他<note place="inline">引</note>蘗多<note place="inline">二</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>野弭縛<note place="inline">引</note>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0924C.0031b" n="0031b"/>
<lb n="0031b01"/>吃質<note place="inline">二合</note>多<note place="inline">三</note>縛曰羅<note place="inline">二合</note>滿娜南迦嚕弭</p>
<lb n="0031b02"/><p>次至心歸依。次真言<note place="inline">印者金剛合掌</note>次施身方便了。
<lb n="0031b03"/>歸命頂禮。施身方便。真言如例。印者。金剛
<lb n="0031b04"/>合掌。投身舒耳。若莊校投者。運心耳。次至心
<lb n="0031b05"/>發願了。歸命頂禮。發菩提心方便真言。次至
<lb n="0031b06"/>心懺悔了。歸命頂禮。次真言<note place="inline">印者。先金剛合掌。大指頭指舒著</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031b07"/><p>次至心隨喜了。次歸命頂禮。次真言<note place="inline">印者。金剛合掌</note>次
<lb n="0031b08"/>至心勸請了。次歸命頂禮。次真言<note place="inline">印者。金剛合掌</note>次
<lb n="0031b09"/>至心奉請誦了。次歸命頂禮。次真言<note place="inline">先作向清印。入內
<lb n="0031b10"/>大指更出舌。頭指鉤召</note>次至心迴向誦了。次歸命頂禮。次
<lb n="0031b11"/>真言如例<note place="inline">印金剛合掌云云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031b12"/><p>次護身。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b13"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;曰羅<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB02915;&CB00135;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;羅捻跛跢<note place="inline">二合引</note>也娑
<lb n="0031b14"/>縛<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0031b15"/><p>次大護身真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b16"/><p type="dharani">唵入&CB00085;羅囊也&CB00292;泮吒</p>
<lb n="0031b17"/><p>次被甲真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b18"/><p type="dharani">唵度比度比迦也度比&CB00425;羅入&CB00085;里寧娑婆賀</p>
<lb n="0031b19"/><p>次結髮。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b20"/><p type="dharani">唵蘇悉地羯哩莎&CB00085;賀</p>
<lb n="0031b21"/><p>次結地界。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b22"/><p type="dharani">唵枳里枳里&CB00085;曰羅<note place="inline">二合</note>縛曰里<note place="inline">二合</note>部律<note place="inline">二合半音</note>
<lb n="0031b23"/>滿馱滿馱吽發吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0031b24"/><p>次結方隅金剛<note n="0031001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">幡＝&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0031001" corr="" resp="【原】">幡</sic>。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b25"/><p type="dharani">唵薩羅薩羅縛曰羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0031002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（&CB00425;羅）&M062485;＋伽【原】</note><sic n="0031002" corr="＆CB00425；羅伽" resp="【原】">伽</sic>羅吽泮吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0031b26"/><p>次置寶座等。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b27"/><p type="dharani">唵毘&CB00757;嚕挪地&CB00292;<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031b28"/><p>次阿者羅吽<note place="inline">三遍</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031b29"/><p type="dharani">唵阿者羅微&CB03272;娑婆賀<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0924C.0031c" n="0031c"/>
<lb n="0031c01"/><p type="dharani">唵迦&CB00757;羅娑婆賀<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031c02"/><p type="dharani">唵囊&CB00757;薩&CB00085;怛他&CB00617;哆南薩羅&CB00085;他欠烏跢&CB00617;
<lb n="0031c03"/>帝娑破羅呬&CB00757;<note n="0031003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔闍〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0031003" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">闍</sic>伽伽囊&CB01894;娑&CB00085;賀<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031c04"/><p>次以我功德力。如來加持力。及以法界力。普
<lb n="0031c05"/>供養而住。</p>
<lb n="0031c06"/><p>次大虛空藏普通供養真言并印。</p>
<lb n="0031c07"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00344;&CB00344;曩三<note place="inline">去</note>婆&CB00085;&CB00085;曰羅<note place="inline">二合</note>斛<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0031c08"/><p>次遏伽以辨事真言持誦。後以部母&CB00057;&CB00057;之。
<lb n="0031c09"/>置於左邊。</p>
<lb n="0031c10"/><p>次部母。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c11"/><p type="dharani">娜牟婆伽婆都烏瑟尼沙耶唵盧盧娑普嚧若
<lb n="0031c12"/>&CB00085;羅帝瑟佗悉陀嚕者&CB00135;薩&CB00085;羅他娑但&CB00135;莎
<lb n="0031c13"/>訶</p>
<lb n="0031c14"/><p>次於寶座上。觀本尊種子字。并結根本印<note place="inline">云
<lb n="0031c15"/>云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031c16"/><p>次轉字成本尊。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c17"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南</p>
<lb n="0031c18"/><p>次欲請本尊。先執香爐。誦真言。淨治空中道
<lb n="0031c19"/>路。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c20"/><p type="dharani">唵蘇悉地迦里入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>里多南多暮羅<note place="inline">二<app><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note>曳
<lb n="0031c21"/>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅滿馱滿馱賀囊賀囊&CB00292;泮吒</p>
<lb n="0031c22"/><p>次發願啟白眾。</p>
<lb n="0031c23"/><p>次奉請本尊。更先想座已也。成就車輅。送本
<lb n="0031c24"/>尊所<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031c25"/><p>寶車輅。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c26"/><p type="dharani">唵都嚕都嚕吽</p>
<lb n="0031c27"/><p>次請車輅。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c28"/><p type="dharani">娜麼悉底哩野<note place="inline">二合</note>地尾<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>南怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB03442;
<lb n="0031c29"/>多<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">引一</note>唵&CB00085;曰郎<note place="inline">二合</note>銀&CB00135;野<note place="inline">三合引</note>羯唎沙
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0924C.0032a" n="0032a"/>
<lb n="0032a01"/>也<note place="inline">二合</note>莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032a02"/><p>次召請奉本尊。真真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a03"/><p type="dharani">唵枳里枳里&CB00085;曰羅吽泮吒<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a04"/><p>次<note n="0032001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原本冠註曰視字更勘</note>視三昧耶。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a05"/><p type="dharani">唵昇羯&CB03740;三&CB00757;&CB00195;莎訶<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a06"/><p>次奉閼伽。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a07"/><p type="dharani">唵藥乞私囊那也見捺羅達弩&CB00425;捨莎訶<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a08"/><p>次奉蓮華座<note place="inline">誦三部真言。獻成用道用</note>。</p>
<lb n="0032a09"/><p type="dharani">唵味羅味羅也莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032a10"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;那&CB00757;味羅也莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032a11"/><p type="dharani">唵縛曰羅味羅也莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032a12"/><p>次陳善來世尊真言。持誦奉獻。</p>
<lb n="0032a13"/><p>次結上方金剛網。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a14"/><p type="dharani">唵尾娑普<note place="inline">二合</note>羅捺落<note place="inline">二合</note>乞刃<note place="inline">二合</note>縛曰羅<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0032a15"/>半惹羅吽泮吒</p><p place="inline">次上下方。</p>
<lb n="0032a16"/><p>次火院真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a17"/><p type="dharani">唵阿三&CB00757;擬&CB00135;吽泮吒</p>
<lb n="0032a18"/><p>次重結大界。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a19"/><p type="dharani">唵昇羯&CB03740;&CB00757;訶三摩焰莎訶<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a20"/><p>次奉塗香。真言曰。</p>
